{"lexicon" 1
 "id" "com.etzhayyim.shomei.bindingRevocation"
 "description" "A SUBJECT-signed retraction of a prior com.etzhayyim.shomei.identityClaim (e.g. a lost wallet, a deleted SNS account, a rotated key). Per ADR-2606072100 (shomei). **G5 consent-bound + revocable**: only the subject can unlink their own factor (signed by the same subject DID). **G10 non-eschatological as-of + Tier-0 \u6C38\u4E45\u8A18\u61B6 (CRITICAL)**: this is an APPEND-ONLY retraction Datom, NOT a deletion \u2014 the original claim's history is permanently retained (\u6C38\u4E45\u8A18\u61B6=\u795E\u306E\u76E3\u8996, no right to erasure). Revocation marks the binding INACTIVE from `revokedAt` onward; downstream aggregation recomputes assurance EXCLUDING revoked factors, but the as-of record that the binding once existed never disappears."
 "defs" {"main" {"type" "record"
 "key" "tid"
 "record" {"type" "object"
 "additionalProperties" false
 "required" ["subjectDid"
 "claimRef"
 "factorKind"
 "reason"
 "revokedAt"
 "subjectSig"]
 "properties" {"subjectDid" {"type" "string"
 "format" "did"
 "description" "DID of the member revoking the binding. MUST equal the subjectDid of the referenced claim (G5: only the owner revokes)."}
 "claimRef" {"type" "string"
 "description" "CID (or AT-URI / tid) of the com.etzhayyim.shomei.identityClaim being revoked."
 "maxLength" 256}
 "factorKind" {"type" "string"
 "enum" ["webauthn"
 "wallet-evm"
 "wallet-btc"
 "sns-github"
 "sns-x"
 "sns-google"
 "sns-apple"
 "gov-mynumber"
 "gov-passport"
 "gov-license"
 "etz-base-membership"
 "etz-adherent-sbt"
 "etz-at-oath"]
 "description" "The factor kind of the revoked claim (mirrors the claim for fast aggregation filtering)."}
 "reason" {"type" "string"
 "enum" ["key-rotated"
 "key-lost"
 "account-closed"
 "compromised"
 "superseded"
 "voluntary"]
 "description" "Reason code for the revocation. Factual operational reasons only \u2014 never a verdict about the person."}
 "revokedAt" {"type" "integer"
 "description" "Unix timestamp (seconds) from which the binding is inactive."}
 "subjectSig" {"type" "string"
 "description" "Ed25519 signature (base64url) by the subject DID's signing key over the CBOR-canonical form of (subjectDid, claimRef, factorKind, reason, revokedAt). G7 no-server-key: only the subject signs."
 "maxLength" 256}}}}}}
